  "title": "Assistant Engineer #77200",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Engineering</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Assistant Engineer / Junior Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tampines</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon to Fri 9AM – 7PM, Sat 9AM – 1PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $2,500 + AWS + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Setup, operate and maintain all measuring equipment, gauges, and fixtures.</li><li>Perform troubleshooting and repair of machinery and equipment</li><li>Programming of CNC lathe machine</li><li>Operate turn mill machines with automatic bar feeder for production</li><li>Monitor production progress and fine tuning the machine to optimize production of components</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum ITE/Diploma qualification</li><li>Prior experience in engineering industries would be an advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77200 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
